    "definition": "Scoring Term Definitions:\n• Corrected Time = Acceleration Run Time + ( DOO * 2 )\n• Tyour - the best Corrected Time for the team\n• Tmin - the lowest Corrected Time recorded for any team\n• Tmax - 150% of Tmin"
