    "page_number": "130",
    "rule_number": "D.10.1.1 Course Design",
    "definition": "Course Design\n• Two pairs of concentric circles in a figure of eight pattern\n• Centers of the circles 18.25 m apart\n• Inner circles 15.25 m in diameter\n• Outer circles 21.25 m in diameter\n• Driving path the 3.0 m wide path between the inner and outer circles"
  }
}

