    "definition": "The Endurance Run Order:\n a. Should be primarily based on the Autocross event finish order\n b. Should include the teams eligible for Endurance which did not compete in the Autocross event.\n c. May be altered by the organizer to accommodate specific circumstances or event considerations"
  },
  "D.12.3.2": {
