    "rule_number": "F.8.7.1",
    "definition": "The combination of the Impact Attenuator assembly and the force to crush or detach all other items forward of the Anti Intrusion plate must not exceed the peak deceleration specified in F.8.8.2\nIgnore light bodywork, light nosecones, and outboard wheel assemblies"
  }
}

