    "definition": "F.8.7.5 Calculation Method\\na. Calculate a failure load for the mounting of the Non Crushable Object(s) from fastener\\nshear, tearout, and/or link buckling\\nb. Add the peak attenuator load from F.8.7.2"
  },
  "F.8.8": {
    "page_number": "47",
